cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.DC, cs.DS

This paper discusses the use of blockchain technologies to create a decentralized review system, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR), database management (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), distributed computing (cs.DC), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.DC, and cs.DS.
